lead_paragraph: Flyhalf Johnny Sexton, who missed Ireland's tour to South Africa earlier this year, has been named in a strong side to take on world champions New Zealand at Soldier Field in Chicago on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Sexton Back as Ireland Name Strong Side to Face All Blacks
